snippet.title: Aquaman movie Why Amber Heard said yes to Mera role in Jason Momoa blockbuster
snippet.description:
Aquaman movie: Why Amber Heard said yes to Mera role in Jason Momoa blockbuster. The star will be seen in the upcoming Aquaman movie alongside Jason Momoa, having first appeared as the character in last year’s Justice League.

In a new interview, she’s revealed what it was that drew her to the role.

“That Mera has her own name,” she told Entertainment Weekly.
